description:
John Zorn, talking in his apartment about his experiences in Japan, Ornette Coleman's music, and so on. Also, a cool Spy vs. Spy live footage !

Featuring appearances by Yale Evelev and Ikue Mori.
title: John Zorn documentary part 2
